FileMutex is similar to sync.RWMutex, but also synchronizes across processes.
On POSIX systems it uses the flock system call. On windows it uses the LockFileEx
and UnlockFileEx system calls. There is no implementation for Plan 9, Solaris, 
or NaCL.

